{"tid":1510161,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"林鄭講得岩,問題癥結的確唔係逃犯條例","createTime":"2019-08-27T05:41:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T06:46:02.000Z","uid":51469,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"183aaa18c8bec3df22fdd675565a3b22cd42782a","tid":1510161,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T05:41:02.000Z","msg":"咁你做過D乜去解決呢個癥結?你有冇講過問題癥結係乜?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477066-20190827.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477066-20190827.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8biwPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=3e1c8277\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477066-20190827.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a8e0b57e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477066-20190827.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥在行政會議前表示，開展對話不代表會容忍暴力，面對暴力持續，唯一應做的是透過法律和執法處理。她說如果因為社會要對話，政府就不執法、容忍暴力和破壞，將會是香港法治的終結。<br />\n<br />\n她又表示，政府不斷回應示威者訴求，所以不是沒回應的問題，而是不接受的問題，政府已接受最重要的訴求，暫緩修例草案，如果草案是問題癥結，混亂情況應該已在兩個月前終止。"},{"pid":"51de575edfc449b54a1535ecbf3dda46122b6462","tid":1510161,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T05:41:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8biwPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=53d89762\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8biwPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=3ad8c2ce